<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Challenge Created - Eighteen</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #bbe4e9;
      --primary-dark: #8fd0d7;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: var(--light);
      color: var(--dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .message-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 480px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-size: 28px;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    
    p {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: var(--dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }
    
    .button:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-dark);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="message-container">
    <h1>Challenge Created!</h1>
    <p>We've sent an invitation to <strong><%= friendEmail %></strong> and will notify you when they accept.</p>
    <a href="/" class="button">Back to Homepage</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>